LOUXOR FOR PETS 
In striking red leather, the Louxor Pet Collar is adorned with a customizable stainless-steel octagon, embodying the timeless elegance of Maison Baccarat. 

Pair it with the matching Louxor Pet Leash, and take your four-legged friend on stylish adventures that celebrate beauty and joy.

@Baccarat, bringing pleasure into the world of our four-legged friends.
